msgid "Atthi ca khvassa akusalamūlaṃ asamucchinnaṃ, tamhā tassa akusalā akusalaṃ pātubhavissati. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an6.62:8.15"
msgid "Evamayaṃ puggalo āyatiṃ parihānadhammo bhavissatī’ti. "
msgstr "This person is still liable to decline in the future … "

msgctxt "an6.62:8.16"
msgid "Evampi kho, ānanda, tathāgatassa purisapuggalo cetasā ceto paricca vidito hoti. "
msgstr "This is how another individual is known to the Realized One … "

msgctxt "an6.62:8.17"
msgid "Evampi kho, ānanda, tathāgatassa purisindriyañāṇaṃ cetasā ceto paricca viditaṃ hoti. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an6.62:8.18"
msgid "Evampi kho, ānanda, tathāgatassa āyatiṃ dhammasamuppādo cetasā ceto paricca vidito hoti. (2) "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc9
msgctxt "an6.62:9.1"
msgid "Idha panāhaṃ, ānanda, ekaccaṃ puggalaṃ evaṃ cetasā ceto paricca pajānāmi: "
msgstr "When I’ve comprehended the mind of a person, I understand: "

msgctxt "an6.62:9.2"
msgid "‘imassa kho puggalassa vijjamānā kusalāpi dhammā akusalāpi dhammā’ti. "
msgstr "‘Both skillful and unskillful qualities are found in this person.’ "

msgctxt "an6.62:9.3"
msgid "Tamenaṃ aparena samayena evaṃ cetasā ceto paricca pajānāmi: "
msgstr "After some time I comprehend their mind and understand: "

msgctxt "an6.62:9.4"
msgid "‘natthi imassa puggalassa vālaggakoṭinittudanamattopi sukko dhammo, samannāgatoyaṃ puggalo ekantakāḷakehi akusalehi dhammehi, kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā apāyaṃ duggatiṃ vinipātaṃ nirayaṃ upapajjissatī’ti. "
msgstr "‘This person has not even a fraction of a hair’s tip of goodness. They have exclusively dark, unskillful qualities. When their body breaks up, after death, they will be reborn in a place of loss, a bad place, the underworld, hell.’ "

msgctxt "an6.62:9.5"
msgid "Seyyathāpi, ānanda, bījāni khaṇḍāni pūtīni vātātapahatāni sukhette suparikammakatāya bhūmiyā nikkhittāni. "
msgstr "Suppose some seeds were broken, spoiled, weather-damaged. They’re sown in a well-prepared, productive field. "

msgctxt "an6.62:9.6"
msgid "Jāneyyāsi tvaṃ, ānanda, nayimāni bījāni vuddhiṃ virūḷhiṃ vepullaṃ āpajjissantī”ti? "
msgstr "Wouldn’t you know that those seeds would not grow, increase, and mature?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an6.62:9.7"
msgid "“Evaṃ, bhante”. "
msgstr "“Yes, sir.” "

